Lenalidomide in Pretreated Patients with Diffuse Large B-Cell Lymphoma: An 
Italian Observational Multicenter Retrospective Study in Daily Clinical 
Practice.

Broccoli A(1), Casadei B(1), Chiappella A(2), Visco C(3), Tani M(4), Cascavilla 
N(5), Conconi A(6), Balzarotti M(7), Cox MC(8), Marino D(9), Goldaniga MC(10), 
